# 🚗 Sandigan Carwash & Car Rental — Development Roadmap

> A living document outlining full-stack development phases, security posture, database management, and production hardening.

---

## 📦 Current System Snapshot (What's Already Built)

| Area | Status | Notes |
|------|--------|-------|
| Public Landing Page | ✅ Done | Hero, services, footer, navbar |
| Public Booking Form (Car Wash) | ✅ Done | Multi-step, reCAPTCHA, time slots, live pricing |
| Employee Dashboard | ✅ Done | Booking table, status management, notifications |
| Booking Modal (View / Edit) | ✅ Done | Status logs, timeline, price badge, service toggles |
| JWT Authentication | ✅ Done | Employees log in via signed token |
| CSRF Protection | ✅ Done | Double-submit cookie pattern |
| Real-time Updates | ✅ Done | Socket.io for instant booking sync |
| Price List System | ✅ Done | DB-driven pricing, auto-seeder, per-vehicle rates |
| Notification System | ✅ Done | Bell icon, unread badge, per-booking alerts |
| Status Lifecycle Logs | ✅ Done | Pending → Confirmed → Queued → Completed / Cancelled |

